\section*{6. (16 points)}

\begin{itemize}
    \item[(a)] Find the equation of a plane determined by the points $(1, -1, 2)$, $(3, 0, 0)$ and $(4, 2, 1)$.
    \item[(b)] Is this plane parallel to the plane $x + y - z = 5$? Show your work, or otherwise justify your answer.
